  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">This arcane branch includes all the enchantments that affect, influence, fortify or weaken the body shape of both the magus and other targets. It is a type of tangible magic, immediate and explicit.</span></p><p><strong>KNOWN SPELLS</strong><br /><span class=\"fontstyle0\">When you chose this secret, you learn the @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.8zT7njvqbpXs4Cel]{Spare the Dying}</span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"> </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">and @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.XvbiNhNqXXIFisIy]{Shocking Grasp}</span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"> </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">cantrips, and when you gain a level in the secret, you learn the corresponding spells indicated by the following table:</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>Cantrips: </strong>@Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.8zT7njvqbpXs4Cel]{Spare the Dying}</span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.XvbiNhNqXXIFisIy]{Shocking Grasp}<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>1st level:</strong> @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.ge3Saet9zPTDyaoL]{Heroism}</span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.7e3QXF10hLNDEdr6]{False Life}<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>2ndlevel:</strong> @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.8RTDOt80u8aBv9qx]{Alter Self}</span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.WahI41a3goVUg0x1]{Enlarge/Reduce}<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>3rd level:</strong> @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.yqUDoxk4x0NWG5Bz]{Slow}</span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.Szvk5FEVQW3uhJi5]{Haste}<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>4th level:</strong> @UUID[Compendium.world.spells-historia.NRb8OowPC5HEFtP1]{Aura of Life}</span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.VtCXMdyM6mAdIJZb]{Death Ward}<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>5th level:</strong> @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.ATo0Eb63TDtnu6iA]{Animate Objects}</span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.CjIq8Ed7bu3vVwT1]{Contagion}</span><br style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:normal;orphans:2;text-align:-webkit-auto;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" /></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>MYSTERIES</strong> <br style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:normal;orphans:2;text-align:-webkit-auto;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" />@Compendium[world.profession-features.DGIHfRkdqmPjIeee]{Founding Mystery: Fortress of the Body}</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">@Compendium[world.profession-features.F2sO4OMJgs4OqFgL]{Major Mystery: Wisdom of the Body}</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">@Compendium[world.profession-features.VrQuIKtyR5QRMuGb]{Greater Mystery: Integrity of the Body}</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">@Compendium[world.profession-features.6VnVlyObPTRhk3sj]{Universal Mystery: Unity of the Body}</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>METAMAGIC OF THE SECRET</strong> <br style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:normal;orphans:2;text-align:-webkit-auto;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" />When you reach 3rd level in this Secret, you became able to modify the spells they can cast, adapting them to your current needs, and learns the following metamagic options. <br style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:normal;orphans:2;text-align:-webkit-auto;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" /></span></p><p>@Compendium[world.profession-features.Y4R545k2y1XxS6er]{Metamagic: Extended Spell}</p><p>@Compendium[world.profession-features.xFBGHjhAlAQBl09J]{Metamagic: Quickened Spell}</p>",
